edu.umn.biomedicus.uima.rtfrewriting

Class SymbolIndexedDocument

  • edu.umn.biomedicus.uima.rtfrewriting.SymbolIndexedDocument

  • public class SymbolIndexedDocument

    A rtf document for modification, contains indices to all the symbols, which are entire control words or characters in the rtf document.
